ChatGPT Implementation Using Django

Features

* Chatbot Interface
* Real-Time User Interaction
* AI-Powered Response Generation
* User-Friendly Web Interface
* Fast and Efficient Query Processing

Tech Used

* Python
* Django
* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

How to Run

1. Install the required packages:

   ```
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

2. Run the Django development server:

   ```
   python manage.py runserver
   ```

3. Open your browser and visit:

   ```
   http://127.0.0.1:8000/
   ```

## Project Description

This mini project implements a ChatGPT-like chatbot using the Django framework. The application provides an interactive web interface where users can submit questions and receive intelligent responses. The project demonstrates web development concepts, user interaction handling, and chatbot integration using Python and Django.

